UID:apostaxis-residency-exhibition-2026@artificialnouveau.github.io
DTSTAMP:20260716T125418Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260726
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260727
SUMMARY:Deadline: APOSTAXIS Artist Residency & Exhibition 2026 (Ukraine / C
 yprus)
DESCRIPTION:APOSTAXIS is an international residency and exhibition programm
 e exploring displacement\, memory\, identity and cultural resilience. It s
 elects four visual artists (three from Ukraine and one from Cyprus) for tw
 o simultaneous 20-day residencies in Ternopil\, Ukraine and Larnaca\, Cypr
 us (6 to 28 October 2026)\, followed by post-production\, a digital exhibi
 tion\, and a curated physical exhibition in Larnaca in January 2027. ELIGI
 BILITY: visual artists from Ukraine and Cyprus with lived experience or fa
 mily heritage connected to displacement\, working in community-engaged or 
 research-based practices (installation\, mixed media\, participatory\, soc
 ial practice\, documentary\, performance\, archive-based work). Artists un
 able to travel due to war-related restrictions or personal circumstances r
 emain eligible via hybrid participation. Fully funded: EUR 1\,800 artist f
 ee (equivalent UAH for Ukrainian artists)\, EUR 300 production budget\, tr
 avel\, accommodation\, meals and curatorial support\; no application fee. 
 Deadline: 26 July 2026.\n\nOrganisation: ZMINA (Ukraine) with Cypriot part
 ner organisation\nLocation: Ternopil\, Ukraine and Larnaca\, Cyprus (hybri
 d participation possible)\nAward: Fully funded: artist fee of EUR 1\,800 (
 including tax\; paid in equivalent UAH for Ukrainian artists)\, EUR 300 pr
 oduction budget\, plus travel\, accommodation\, meals and curatorial suppo
 rt. No application fee.\nDuration: 20-day residency\, 6 to 28 October 2026
 \, with a group exhibition in Larnaca in January 2027\n\nMore: https://art
 infoland.com/opportunities/apostaxis-artist-residency-2026-ukraine-cyprus?
 utm_source=artificialnouveaugrantdesk&utm_medium=referral
URL:https://artinfoland.com/opportunities/apostaxis-artist-residency-2026-u
 kraine-cyprus?utm_source=artificialnouveaugrantdesk&utm_medium=referral
LOCATION:Ternopil\, Ukraine and Larnaca\, Cyprus (hybrid participation poss
 ible)
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR
